        <li><em>Limits of Teichmuller geodesics in the Bers boundary (working title), with Pranav Haridas (in preparation).
      
        <li><em>Counting rational curves in the complex projextive plane with an ordinary m-fold point</em>,
            with Indranil Biswas, Apratim Choudhury, Ritwik Mukherjee and Anantadulal Paul (in preparation). </li>
      
        <li><em>The intersection matrices of X_0(p^r) and some applications</em>; 
            with Debargha Banerjee and Priyanka Majumder 
            (<a href="https://arxiv.org/abs/2210.08866" target="new">arxiv</a>).</li>
      
	<li><em>Elliptic Gromov-Witten Invariants of del Pezzo Surfaces</em>; with Nilkantha Das, 
            <b>J. Gökova Geom. Topol.</b> (<a href="https://arxiv.org/abs/1901.00839" target="new">arxiv</a>,
