	   Nilkantha Das to calculate elliptic Gromov-Witten invariants for del Pezzo surfaces.</p>

        <li><em>Semi-stable models of modular curves X_0(p^2) and some arithmetic applications</em>; 
            with Debargha Banerjee, <b>Israel J. Math</b>, (<a href="https://arxiv.org/pdf/1802.06968.pdf" target="new">arxiv</a>,
